Cerberus and Innkeepers Settle Dispute Over Hotel Deal

-- B y   T i f f a n y   K a r y
-- 
2011-10-19T17:26:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/cerberus-and-innkeepers-settle-dispute-over-hotel-deal.html
Cerberus Capital Management LP and
 Innkeepers USA Trust  settled a dispute over whether a U.S.
economic decline justified the buyout firm’s end of a deal to
buy 64 of Innkeepers’ hotels. The settlement values the hotels
at over $1 billion.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Pickering at 
 jpickering@bloomberg.net  